messages.title: The SNP have failed
messages.content: Only the Liberal Democrats will fight for a fair deal for Scotland.

issues.health: Despite higher NHS spending in the rest of the UK, the SNP have cut health spending in Scotland, experts say. SNP MISSED CANCER TREATMENT TARGETS MISSED HOSPITALS IN BED SHORTAGE CRISIS ALL UNDERFUNDING LEADING TO RISE IN BED BLOCKING REST OF UK
